  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If there were a few thousand-- 10,000-- what is this about 4 million people?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I guess that may be why it-- it's-- we feel so strongly about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Is there anything else you want to say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if you want to add anything about my years between '42 and-- and '48, in Israel, I can add to it some-- something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you want to cut here--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I'll add a little bit of my history in-- in Israel-- Palestine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Specially, I want to emphasize, like we were talking about, and I mentioned right in the beginning, that my grandmother sending me to that cheder, which my father was opposed, had big [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] results later, when we came to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they asked-- and they were asking the children, were you religious at home?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you want to go to religious institutes or to not religious institute?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even so, I knew very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remembered that my father wasn't religious at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But for somehow, the weight of my grandmother, which I loved dearly-- I can't even mention that name without [DRINKS] getting emotional about it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It made me choose to go to a religion place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went to one place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I felt that it's not religious enough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I want to go to more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were-- we were in groups of children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was 10, at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I organized a group of 10 children, that we came, and we demanded that we want to be transferred to a more religion placing.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
